---
import BaseLayout from '../components/layout/BaseLayout.astro';
import '../styles/prose.css';
---

<BaseLayout title="About" description="About the author.">
  <div class="page-wrapper">
    <article class="prose about-prose">
      <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      <h1>About</h1>

      <p>
        This site is a home for long-form technical writing: research notes, paper digests,
        conceptual essays, and occasional working drafts that are clearer than a thread and
        lighter than a formal publication.
      </p>

      <p>
        For non-technical writing, see the sister Substack
        <a href="https://approximatelycorrect.substack.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Approximately Correct
        </a>.
      </p>

      <h2>What you'll find here</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Machine learning essays that privilege first principles over hype</li>
        <li>Technical notes connecting economics, physics, biology, and computation</li>
        <li>Reference-style posts with math, code, and citations designed for careful reading</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>Elsewhere</h2>
      <p>
        Non-technical essays and broader reflections live on
        <a href="https://approximatelycorrect.substack.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          Approximately Correct
        </a>.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .page-wrapper {
    padding-top: var(--space-16);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-20);
  }

  .about-prose h1 {
    margin-top: var(--space-2);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }
</style>
